These are instructions for setting up the deposit application for development. 

00. install setuptools http://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools
01. easy_install django
02. easy_install wsgi_intercept
03. easy_install httplib2
04. easy_install pysqlite
06. svn co https://rdc.lctl.gov/svn/transfer/deposit/trunk deposit
06. cp deposit/conf/dev-settings.py deposit/deposit/settings.py
07. mkdir /tmp/deposit_storage # or whatever STORAGE is set to in settings.py
08. cd deposit/deposit
09. python manage.py syncdb
10. python manage.py test
11. python manage.py runserver
